languages.text: "Этот ашмаг..." {n}Голос Джай пронизан гневом и жаждой мести.{/n} "Нет, пока ему от меня еще кое-что нужно. Так что мертвы не все — по крайней мере, для него же будет лучше, если это так. Где он, Окти? Говори!"

languages.text: “那个坏种……”{n}婕伊的声音中充满了愤怒与复仇的渴望。{/n}“不，他还想从我这里得到什么，所以不是所有人都死了。如果留下一部分活口，对他来说是更好的选择。他在什么地方，小奥？告诉我！”
languages.original_text: "That ashmag..." {n}Jae's voice is full of anger and thirst for vengeance.{/n} "No, there's still something he needs from me. So not all of them are dead, or at any rate, it will be better for him if some aren't. Where is he, Octy? Speak!"

traits.locale_text: “那个坏家伙……”{n}婕伊的声音中充满了愤怒与复仇的渴望。{/n}“不，他还想从我这里得到什么，所以不是所有人都死了。如果留下一部分活口，对他来说是更好的选择。他在什么地方，小奥？告诉我！”
traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: 「アッシュマグめ…」{n}ジェイの声は、怒りと復讐願望に満ちていた。{/n}「いや、彼はまだ俺を必要としてる。全員が死んだわけじゃない。状態はともかく。いや、何人かは生き残っている方がいいはずだ。で、奴は一体どこに行っちまったんだ、オクティ？答えろ！」
languages.original_text: "That ashmag..." {n}Jae's voice is full of anger and thirst for vengeance.{/n} "No, there's still something he needs from me. So not all of them are dead, or at any rate, it will be better for him if some aren't. Where is he, Octy? Speak!"

languages.text: «Ese ashmag...». {n}La voz de Jae está llena de ira y sed de venganza.{/n} «No, todavía hay algo que necesita de mí. No todos están muertos, o más bien, será mejor para él que algunos no lo estén. ¿Dónde está, Octy? ¡Di!».
languages.original_text: "That ashmag..." {n}Jae's voice is full of anger and thirst for vengeance.{/n} "No, there's still something he needs from me. So not all of them are dead, or at any rate, it will be better for him if some aren't. Where is he, Octy? Speak!"

languages.text: "Dieser Ashmag ..." {n}Jaes Stimme ist voller Wut und Rachedurst.{/n} "Nein, er braucht noch etwas von mir. Es sind also nicht alle tot. Oder zumindest wäre es für ihn besser, wenn es einige nicht sind. Wo ist er, Octy? Redet!"
languages.original_text: "That ashmag..." {n}Jae's voice is full of anger and thirst for vengeance.{/n} "No, there's still something he needs from me. So not all of them are dead, or at any rate, it will be better for him if some aren't. Where is he, Octy? Speak!"

languages.text: {n}La voix de Jae tremble de colère et de soif de vengeance.{/n} « Ce sale ashmag... Non, il a encore besoin de moi, ce qui veut dire qu'ils ne sont pas tous morts ; du moins, ça vaudrait mieux pour lui. Où est-il, Octa ? Dis-le-moi ! »
languages.original_text: "That ashmag..." {n}Jae's voice is full of anger and thirst for vengeance.{/n} "No, there's still something he needs from me. So not all of them are dead, or at any rate, it will be better for him if some aren't. Where is he, Octy? Speak!"

traits.speaker: JaeCompanion

languages.text: "Vay külboğaz..." {n}Jae'ın öfkesi ve intikam arzusu, sesine yansıyor.{/n} "Yok, benimle işi henüz bitmiş değil. Yani hepsini öldürmüş olduğunu sanmıyorum. En azından öldürmediyse işi daha kolay olur. Nerede o Octy? Söyle!"
languages.original_text: "That ashmag..." {n}Jae's voice is full of anger and thirst for vengeance.{/n} "No, there's still something he needs from me. So not all of them are dead, or at any rate, it will be better for him if some aren't. Where is he, Octy? Speak!"

traits.locale_text: "Vay külboğaz..." {n}Jae'ın sesinden öfkesi ve intikam arzusu yansıyor.{/n} "Yok, benimle işi henüz bitmiş değil. Yani hepsini öldürmüş olduğunu sanmıyorum. En azından öldürmediyse işi daha kolay olur. Nerede o Octy? Cevap ver bana!"
traits.speaker: JaeCompanion
